<a class="jxr_linenumber" name="L426" href="#L426">426</a>     <em class="jxr_javadoccomment">/**</em>
<a class="jxr_linenumber" name="L427" href="#L427">427</a> <em class="jxr_javadoccomment">     * Rounds the given value to the specified number of decimal places.</em>
<a class="jxr_linenumber" name="L428" href="#L428">428</a> <em class="jxr_javadoccomment">     * The value is rounded using the given method which is any method defined</em>
<a class="jxr_linenumber" name="L429" href="#L429">429</a> <em class="jxr_javadoccomment">     * in {@link BigDecimal}.</em>
